{"tid":1318334,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你屋企人係深藍請入嚟睇睇","createTime":"2019-07-15T02:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T10:30:48.000Z","uid":17379,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c58ccf1b685c9c3aaf20b098f9aa6401d319cbd8","tid":1318334,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"我已經唔會再同屋企人嘈黃定藍 對與錯<br />\n我同佢地講： <br />\n<br />\n對唔住 第時屋企唔會有孫仔孫女比你地抱 因為我對香港未來已經無信心 係香港生活壓力太大 比唔到希望下一代 <br />\n<br />\n對唔住 第時我會離開香港移民 香港已經唔適合生活 只淨下生存 打工令我有焦慮<br />\n<br />\n對唔住 我唔會結婚 我唔想一家幾口連埋老婆仔女逼埋係幾百尺嘅地方 港地價唔係我同你兩代人負擔得到（如果你住公屋）比唔到幸福另一掌同兩老<br />\n<br />\n之後佢地就「唉～」咗一聲之後靜咗無出聲 過幾日睇新聞反應都無咁大 你地可以試下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：係真實想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdae4472073e024d07ffc1f22e2568ea79013110","tid":1318334,"uid":17379,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:20:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286862583f0f8132db7ca187eb70356929864e8b","tid":1318334,"uid":219266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pu4Bn4Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpu4Bn4Y.gif&h=1e49a9e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97ab0d94c19e4b5d055c3c91c093bd7c20234e3e","tid":1318334,"uid":97675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"對我老母無用 佢直頭覺得香港玩完接受左事實咁 又話有得走出去好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbc9847b3f93e7e72df5d6cfb42779f6ede01d6","tid":1318334,"uid":80965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"97ab0d94c19e4b5d055c3c91c093bd7c20234e3e","tid":1318334,"uid":97675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"對我老母無用 佢直頭覺得香港玩完接受左事實咁 又話有得走出去好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkg